Class MiniMU.MiniMUListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.happybrackets.device.sensors.MiniMU.MiniMUListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SensorListener
    Enclosing class:
    MiniMU

    public abstract static class MiniMU.MiniMUListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements SensorListener
    Specific listener for the MiniMu sensor. Listens to various MiniMu data: accelerometer, gyro, mag, tem. There is also an imu() callback which receives them all.
